   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Modbus is a serial communications protocol, the NMC supports Modbus
RTU (also called Modbus serial) and Modbus TCP/IP (also called Modbus
TCP). If using Modbus serial for the NMC, the RS-485 communication
should be wired with full duplex over a 4-wire bus.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For more details about the wiring of the Modbus serial, see <xref href="NMC_Modbus_Wiring_Diagrams_CPT_0000354936.dita"
               scope="local"
               type="concept"
